productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Spratly Islands and I bought one.
My neighbor Montserrat has one of these. She works as a circus performer and she says it looks shriveled.
The box this comes in is 3 yard by 6 light-year and weights 15 gram!!!
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
